This paper discusses the management of all-flash storage systems in datacenters, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) model, which is related to the field of Statistics (cs.ST) and Database Systems (cs.DB). The paper also mentions the optimization of workload allocation decisions, which is related to the field of Systems and Control (cs.SY) and Architecture (cs.AR).
